An absolutely magnificent monument, a testament to Rome's eternal splendor! The Pantheon is a marvel of engineering and architecture, whose majestic dome has defied time for nearly two thousand years. Entering this immense dome open to the sky is a breathtaking experience, where one feels all the power and harmony of Antiquity. Every stone breathes history, from the monumental columns to the illustrious tombs, including that of Raphael. Day and night, this place exudes a unique aura, both mystical and solemn. A must-see, which leaves an unforgettable imprint on the heart of every traveler!
